org.ahocorasick.trie

类 PayloadMatchToken<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.ahocorasick.trie.PayloadToken<T>
      • org.ahocorasick.trie.PayloadMatchToken<T>
  • 类型参数:
    T - The Type of the emitted payloads.

    public class PayloadMatchToken<T>
extends PayloadToken<T>
    Container for a token ("the fragment") that can emit a type of payload.

    This token indicates a matching search term was found, so isMatch() always returns true.

    作者:
    Daniel Beck
